      • getEntitiesByEntityId

        public <T,S> java.util.List<T> getEntitiesByEntityId​(java.lang.Class<T> returnType,
                                                     java.util.List<S> linkList,

                                                     java.lang.String returnTypeIdName,
                                                     java.lang.String searchTypeIdName,
                                                     java.lang.String id)
        Get list of A-type entities by id of B-type entity from a list of n-to-m relations between A and B Returns list of POJOs of entity type A.
        Parameters:
        returnType - Class of POJOs to return (entity type A).
        linkList - List of n-to-m relations between A and B entities.
        metaAggregator - Aggregator object knowing list of returnType POJOs (type A).
        returnTypeIdName - Name of foreign key for return types (A) in the n-to-m relations linkList.
        searchTypeIdName - Name of foreign key for search type (B) in the n-to-m relations linkList.
        Returns:
        List of entities of type A by given entity id of type B.
